data.description: 10 min walk to Madeira beach: bright and light, newly remodeled in 2021. Beautiful, private, Furnished 2 bedroom beach house. Each half of this home is its own updated 1 bedroom unit, with private fenced backyards. Great to live on one side, and provide a  beach rental or a mother-in law suite on the other side. Remodeled with new quartz countertops, shaker cabinets, new electrical throughout and updated plumbing, never run out of hot water with tankless electric water heaters and ...turn key.. ..Each side with a back door to their own private backyards. Plenty of parking in front for up 4 cars. Walk to  the sugary, sandy beach on the Gulf of Mexico, Caddys, coffee shop, Petes Sushi , Daiquiri Shack, Post Office,  Johns Pass , shops, restaurants and more!
